TO INSTALL:
1. git clone git://github.com/tomoyuki28jp/autotest-gnome-notify.git ~/.autotest.d
2. ln -s ~/.autotest.d/.autotest ~/

NOTE:
I've only tested on the following environment:
- Ubuntu 10.04
- notify-send 0.4.5
- rails 3.0.0
- autotest 4.4.2

